➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《狮子桥》
http://www.sohu.com/a/412259723_100115135	41011
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200809/e058bf59c9c24c3db1f2a68bacdc9946.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《狮子桥》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">找了很久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也没有找到你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那桥栏上爬着狮子的古桥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早已荡然无存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过还好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>市井烟火气依然亲切</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这里虽然不再繁华</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老南京的舌尖美味地道未变</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶尔也会听见姑娘们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说几句官话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在三三俩俩的过客中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店肆的小二在吆喝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">细雨中的南京又到了撑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灯的时刻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200809/60e7b8a9ec35486594827dc1c8704474.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
