➜【星连文学社】广东诗人小隐：山中寻幽
http://www.sohu.com/a/412259884_100115135	41250
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200809/27a20f6a9c0d4c2ca1026aca3c317bee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>山中寻幽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">初秋暑未消，向晚暮云燎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荷浅林中暗，花深雨后娇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼寻三径水，鸟宿半山樵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天色尚为早，心幽景寂寥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200809/fe695d98006d46f48f8e0052aace4b8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200809/63d26b4d13924b338c6877828e258cc4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
