➜【星连文学社】湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：游 梦
http://www.sohu.com/a/412268858_100115135	46864
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200809/e79f17033eae4430ad4ece44e01082cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>游 梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彩虹迷离，摇笑树柔逸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抛媚眼的瀑布托举一只动人鸟儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拨弄羽毛，饥饿撩衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人群中开始对它接连不断地喂食</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撒出一把把金色谷粒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冷不及防，秃鹫勐然出击</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一缕黒绸缠绕，掳去了施善的载体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痛跌在明山瞳仁里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>惊月泣无声，血泪细雨淋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一块块枯草地湿里渐茵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沦陷在馅饼泥淖洼池</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千斤腿脚难移动，抻不开烟泥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竟力举一劲，挣扎一搏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拔出梦，跳出晨曦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">收起汗夜慈悲陷阱的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年8月9日 下午</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
